Users Tax
================================================================================

Summary
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Users Tax module lets the admin to associate users with a taxonomy term. 


Requirements
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Users Tax Term module requires the Taxonomy (core).

Optional : Email Node module 


Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Copy the Userstax folder to sites/all/modules or to a site-specific
   modules folder.
2. Go to Administer > Site building > Modules and enable the Users Tax     module.


Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1.Go to Administer -> Associate users with taxonomy on the left sidebar . Alternatively , go to Administer -> By Module -> Associate users with taxonomy in the Users Tax fieldset .
3. Select the users through the checkboxes and select the taxonomy terms from the respective vocabularies .(You can also select multiple terms by pressing "Ctrl" and selecting the terms)
4. Click on Submit . 

Note : Select 'None' if you do not wish to associate any taxonomy term from a particular vocabulary


